<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>MakeUp</title>


    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Muli|Source+Sans+Pro:400,700,700i&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>

	<nav id="nav">
				<ul class="container">
					<li><a href="/types">Home</a></li>
				</ul>
			</nav>


	<div id="header">
				<span class="logo icon fa-paper-plane"></span>
				<h1>Welcome to the MAKEUP API</h1>
        <br>
      <%= link_to image_tag("maquillaje2.png",  :class => 'dock-item') %>

			</div>

		<!-- Main -->
			<div id="main">

				<header class="major container medium">
					<h2> where you will find different 
					<br />
				types of makeup at affordable prices.
				</header>

				
				
				<footer class="major container medium">
					<h3>I could stop buying makeup</h3>
					<p> but the truth is that I do not usually give up easily.</p>
				
				</footer>

			</div>



<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body1">
        <h4 class="card-title">Blush</h4>
       <center> <p class="card-text">Develop a pink tinge in the face.</p>
       <center><%= link_to "Category", category_Blush_path(:type => "blush"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body2">
         <h4 class="card-title">Bronzer</h4>
         <center> <p class="card-text">It is a variant of the blush that serves to give a tan or tan to the skin.</p>
          <center> <%= link_to "Category", category_Bronzer_path(:type => "bronzer"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<br>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body3">
          <h4 class="card-title">Eyebrow</h4>
         <center> <p class="card-text">To give a style of curves to your eyebrows.</p>
          <center><%= link_to "Category", category_EyeBrow_path(:type => "eyebrow"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body4">
            <h4 class="card-title">Eyeliner</h4>
           <center> <p class="card-text">It is the cosmetic used to make the outline, a line with strong intensity that defines the eyes.</p>
            <center><%= link_to "Category", category_EyeLiner_path(:type => "eyeliner"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<br>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body5">
           <h4 class="card-title">EyeShadow</h4>
          <center> <p class="card-text">the shadows are to give more intensity to your makeup and that your eyes enhance more.</p>
           <center> <%= link_to "Category", category_EyeShadow_path(:type => "eyeshadow"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body6">
             <h4 class="card-title">Foundation</h4>
             <center> <p class="card-text">The one that we always apply after the moisturizer as a previous step to face and lip makeup.</p>
              <center>  <%= link_to "Category", category_Foundation_path(:type => "foundation"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
           </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>

<br>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body7">
            <h4 class="card-title">LipLiner</h4>
           <center> <p class="card-text">This makeup allows you to delineate your lips to give it a unique shape.</p>
            <center> <%= link_to "Category", category_LipLiner_path(:type => "lip_liner"), :class => 'btn btn-primary' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body8">
             <h4 class="card-title">Mascara</h4>
            <center>  <p  class="card-text">This makeup allows you to give volume to your lashes for a sensational look.</h5>
             <center> <%= link_to "Category", category_Mascara_path(:type => "mascara"), :class => 'btn btn-primary ' %></center>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>Posted by: Maria Jose Chavarria Bravo.</p>
  <p>Contact information: <a href="marita.jose.ch@gmail.com">
  marita.jose.ch@gmail.com</a></p>
</footer>



</body> 
  </html>







